{"sn1.41:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.41 ","sn1.41:0.2":"5. Adittavagga ","sn1.41:0.3":"Adittasutta ","sn1.41:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","sn1.41:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava savatthiyam viharati jetavane anathapindikassa arame. ","sn1.41:1.3":"Atha kho annatara devata abhikkantaya rattiya abhikkantavanna kevalakappam jetavanam obhasetva yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthasi. ","sn1.41:1.4":"Ekamantam thita kho sa devata bhagavato santike ima gathayo abhasi: ","sn1.41:2.1":"“Adittasmim agarasmim, ","sn1.41:2.2":"yam niharati bhajanam; ","sn1.41:2.3":"Tam tassa hoti atthaya, ","sn1.41:2.4":"no ca yam tattha dayhati. ","sn1.41:3.1":"Evam adittako loko, ","sn1.41:3.2":"jaraya maranena ca; ","sn1.41:3.3":"Niharetheva danena, ","sn1.41:3.4":"dinnam hoti sunihatam. ","sn1.41:4.1":"Dinnam sukhaphalam hoti, ","sn1.41:4.2":"nadinnam hoti tam tatha; ","sn1.41:4.3":"Cora haranti rajano, ","sn1.41:4.4":"aggi dahati nassati. ","sn1.41:5.1":"Atha antena jahati, ","sn1.41:5.2":"Sariram sapariggaham; ","sn1.41:5.3":"Etadannaya medhavi, ","sn1.41:5.4":"Bhunjetha ca dadetha ca; ","sn1.41:5.5":"Datva ca bhutva ca yathanubhavam, ","sn1.41:5.6":"Anindito saggamupeti thanan”ti. "}